<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7361> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7361" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Aed. Cur. 44. Note that while the spelling in ILS 6075 favors a relatively early date, both Dessau and Münzer remain uncertain whether the aedile in question was the consul of 23 (RE no. 92) or his father (91). Reference to Terentius (2). Tr. pl. 54, is probably irrelevant, since a Varro Murena would hardly be referred to as simply Terentius. (TJC)[204]" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5965> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5965" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Named as colleagues in an inscription found at Rome (CIL 12.2.2514ILS 6075) and dated probably in or before 44." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5682> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5682" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "A Pompeian, who was present at the conference on the Apsus river (Caes. BC 3.19.4)." .
